message.body: Hi Gabi, What do you make of Phinn? And ideas on how to improve things? Or am I being a worry wart? I feel like you're good at this stuff. If you have ideas we could try to discuss with them on Tuesday
I think he's just stressed and sleep-deprived, i've heard him say very similar things the past few years.
I don't know why but my iMessages to you won't work. Weird.
Just fixed, i turned it off to send a mass text for the fundraiser

Oh cool. So Phinn. I just don't remember him being this strung out during rehearsals. He seems so checked out and it's not usually like this. I don't know. I don't know how he can co create if he's half asleep
I felt really bad for some of the auditioners. Oh well we can chat Tuesday. Hopefully he can work something out so he can be present and fresh on Sundays
